@startuml
title interview-analysis-report - 면접 분석 리포트 생성 Celery Worker 내부 구조

skinparam backgroundColor #FEFEFE
skinparam defaultFontSize 11
skinparam componentStyle rectangle
skinparam packageStyle rectangle
skinparam component {
  BackgroundColor #E8F4FD
  BorderColor #2196F3
}
skinparam component<<external>> {
  BackgroundColor #ECEFF1
  BorderColor #607D8B
}
skinparam component<<llm>> {
  BackgroundColor #FFF3E0
  BorderColor #FB8C00
}
skinparam component<<aws>> {
  BackgroundColor #FFF3E0
  BorderColor #FB8C00
}

queue "Redis\n(analysis queue)" as Redis <<external>>
component "Backend SSE\n(진행 이벤트 게시)" as BE_SSE <<external>>
database "PostgreSQL\n(SQLAlchemy 직접 접근)" as DB <<external>>
component "LLM Gateway" as LLM <<llm>>
component "Lambda\nvoice-analyzer\n(boto3.invoke RequestResponse)" as VALam <<aws>>
database "S3 (scaled-audio)" as S3 <<external>>

package "interview-analysis-report/" {
  component "celery_app.py\nconfig.py" as Cfg

  package "tasks/" {
    component "generate_report.py\n(BaseTask — ReportGenerator entry)" as TaskMain
  }

  package "services/" {
    component "ReportGenerator\n(orchestrator)\n5 단계 파이프라인" as ReportGen
    component "Loader\n(Session · Turn · Resume · JD\nfrom PostgreSQL)" as Loader
    component "VoiceAnalysisInvoker\n(parallel Lambda.invoke)" as VAInv
    component "AnalysisContext.build\n(컨텍스트 통합)" as CtxBuild
    component "LLMAnalyzer\n(5 카테고리 점수 + 피드백)\nstructured output" as LLMAna
    component "Repository\n(save InterviewAnalysisReport\nSQLAlchemy upsert)" as Repo
  }

  package "db/" {
    component "session\n(SQLAlchemy engine)\nmodels (read-only mirror)" as DBLayer
  }

  package "utils/" {
    component "Logging\nProgress event publisher\nMetric helpers" as Utils
  }
}

Redis --> TaskMain : pull task (session_id)
TaskMain --> ReportGen : run(session_id)
ReportGen --> Loader : load_session()
Loader --> DBLayer
DBLayer --> DB : SELECT (join Turn · Resume · JD)

ReportGen --> VAInv : per-turn audio_key 병렬 호출
VAInv --> VALam : invoke
VALam --> S3 : GET .wav
VALam --> VAInv : {speed, fillers, silence, volume}

ReportGen --> CtxBuild : assemble(turns + voice + meta)
CtxBuild --> LLMAna : full context

LLMAna --> LLM : prompt (5 category schema)
LLM --> LLMAna : scores · feedback · strengths · improvements

ReportGen --> Repo : save(report)
Repo --> DBLayer
DBLayer --> DB : UPSERT InterviewAnalysisReport

ReportGen --> Utils : publish progress
Utils --> Redis : Channel Layer event
Redis --> BE_SSE

footer interview-analysis-report/ — 5 단계 파이프라인 · SQLAlchemy 직접 접근 · 병렬 Lambda · LLM 5 카테고리 점수
@enduml
